      "content": "i'm just trying to figure out if i'm being paranoid here. if i only have like 4 or 5 oz of wine, it's barely any alcohol at all. would it be okay if i just took a half dose of the zolpidem instead to balance it out? that way i'm not taking a full dose on top of the wine. it seems like a much safer way to handle it if i really need the help to sleep.",
